description:
This is not only a ttttribute, but also a Window ggggiveaway!  

To celebrate HEN500K I decided to make something fun for the community, so I’ll be giving away Window Still Life 056, aka the glitchy window, 3 high edition windows and 2 skeles  
+ There will be 5 swaps of 100 editions each. 1 edition = 1 Raffle Ticket.
+ Each time a batch of 100 editions is sold out, a raffle will begin among the owners of said editions. 
+ But if you didn’t win a raffle, don’t worry! Window Still Life 056 will be raffled among everyone who owns an edition once all 500 editions sell out!

These are the objkts you can win:

1. Raffle will be for Window 066
2. Raffle for Window  084
3. Raffle for Window 084
4. Raffle for Skele 🧀🧈🍔🍇🌻🔥🦴🪵
5. Raffle: Skele ⛷🟡🐦📓🌭🌎🥤🍖 

And of course, because NFTs without royalties would be nothing, I’ll transfer jjjjjohn 10% of the final income to mirror their usual royalties on windows.  

Best of luck and thank you HEN community for the amazing last couple of months. This is just the beginning!
